  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project develops digital classrooms-in-a-box for distribution to Amazon River schools, and trains teachers to use them.  River schools are small single-classroom rural schools that serve impoverished students along the Amazon River.  We are building and deploying kits with smartphones and Raspberry Pis (plus our learning system Agavi) and helping local educators develop appropriate learning activities and resources.</narrative>
